# Validation & Launch Checklist

## 1. Feature Flows
- [ ] Signup / login / logout work end-to-end
- [ ] Core user journeys complete and tested
- [ ] Critical errors surfaced with clear messages

## 2. Security & Data
- [ ] All user data scoped by userId
- [ ] Auth checks on protected routes
- [ ] No hardcoded secrets; env vars used
- [ ] `.env.example` documents required vars

## 3. Performance
- [ ] Lighthouse audit acceptable
- [ ] React.lazy for large components where appropriate
- [ ] DB queries select only needed fields; indexes in place

## 4. UX
- [ ] Empty states, loading, error states handled
- [ ] Error Boundaries for major sections
- [ ] Meta tags, favicon, responsive layout

## 5. Pre-Launch
- [ ] `pnpm audit` clean
- [ ] Staging smoke test passed
- [ ] Production env vars set and verified
